tool_description: Online code sandbox API to run your code in 200+ languages.
name: RunIt API
title: RunIt API

api_list.name: Execute Code
api_list.description:
Runs your code in a sandboxed environment.

**Parameters:**

- code: Code to run (string) **(required)**
- input: Value of stdin (user input) (string or null) (optional)
- lang: Language id (from /languages endpoint) (string) **(required)**
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://runit-api.p.rapidapi.com/execute"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "runit-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
